msgid "# Stop-ClusterGroup"
msgstr "# 停止集群组（Stop-ClusterGroup）"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Stops one or more clustered roles on a failover cluster."
msgstr "在故障转移集群中，停止一个或多个群集角色（clustered roles）的运行。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `Stop-ClusterGroup` cmdlet stops one or more clustered roles, also known as resource groups,\n"
"on a failover cluster."
msgstr "`Stop-ClusterGroup` cmdlet 用于停止故障转移集群中的一个或多个群集角色（也称为资源组）。"

msgid ""
"If maintenance on a clustered role is needed, the clustered role can be stopped in an orderly\n"
"fashion by using this cmdlet."
msgstr "如果需要对集群角色进行维护，可以使用此cmdlet以有序的方式停止该集群角色。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Stop a clustered role on the local cluster"
msgstr "#### 示例 1：在本地集群中停止一个集群角色（clustered role）"

msgid ""
"This example stops the clustered role, or resource group, called "
"`FileServer1` on the local cluster."
msgstr "这个示例会停止名为 `FileServer1` 的集群角色或资源组在本地集群上的运行。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to run this cmdlet. If the input for this parameter is\n"
"`.` or it is omitted, then the cmdlet runs on the local cluster."
msgstr "指定用于运行此 cmdlet 的集群名称。如果该参数的输入值为`.` 或被省略，则 cmdlet 将在本地集群上运行。"

msgid "Specifies that locked groups are ignored when running the cmdlet."
msgstr "指定在运行此cmdlet时忽略已锁定的组。"

msgid "Specifies the clustered role to stop."
msgstr "指定要停止运行的集群角色。"

msgid "Specifies the name of the clustered role to stop."
msgstr "指定要停止运行的集群角色的名称。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the time in seconds to wait for the cmdlet. If the **Wait** parameter isn't specified,\n"
"then the cmdlet waits for completion. If `-Wait 0` is specified, then the call is initiated and the\n"
"cmdlet returns without waiting."
msgstr ""
"指定等待该 cmdlet 完成的时间（以秒为单位）。如果未指定 **Wait** 参数，那么 cmdlet 会一直等待直到完成。如果指定了 `-Wait"
" 0`，则调用会被立即启动，且 cmdlet 会在不等待的情况下立即返回结果。"

